{"tid":531354,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台北宜蘭行程求批","createTime":"2018-01-16T17:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T05:38:11.000Z","uid":104360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dee49df0c1d5b024702b73044d7dddd65ac21c0e","tid":531354,"uid":104360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"黎緊月尾會去8日台北同宜蘭<br />\n主要都係想hea下同食下野<br />\n初步諗左d行程 希望各位巴絲俾d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n11點機去桃園機場<br />\n去到應該喺酒店hea陣 然後食野<br />\n西門町/附近有冇咩好食既野推介<br />\n生日想食好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住西門町<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n台北--&gt;九份--&gt;基隆--&gt;台北<br />\n住西門町<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n暫時未諗到<br />\n住西門町<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n台北--&gt;礁溪<br />\n住礁溪<br />\n<br />\nDay 5<br />\n礁溪--&gt;羅東林場--&gt;羅東夜市--&gt;礁溪<br />\n住礁溪<br />\n<br />\nDay 6<br />\n礁溪--&gt;蘭陽博物館--&gt;台北<br />\n住西門町<br />\n<br />\nDay 7<br />\n酒店--&gt;永康街--&gt;101大樓--&gt;寧夏夜市--&gt;酒店<br />\n住西門町<br />\n<br />\nDay 8<br />\n酒店--&gt; ? --&gt;華西街夜市--&gt;機場<br />\n夜晚10點機返香港<br />\n諗住早早地掃下街先返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n有冇d景點可以推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身都去過幾次台北 其實開始有d悶<br />\n喺台北入面既景點大部分都係就人地先去<br />\n如果冇就應該會摺喺酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 4-6<br />\n想去埋宜蘭個幾米公園到此一遊下<br />\n應該放邊一日好<br />\n初步預計day 4中午搭火車去礁溪<br />\nday 6 4點幾火車返台北 (巴士驚塞車)<br />\n另外去宜蘭洗唔洗book定飛(閒日去同返)<br />\n<br />\nDay 7<br />\n如果行下大安森林公園好唔好<br />\n上網睇個公園好似幾靚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 8<br />\n朝早又係諗唔到去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要check out又冇得留喺酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得半日又去唔到d咩<br />\n<br />\n同埋個行程其實會唔會hea左d<br />\n雖然本意都係想休息下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該哂大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1024c6cd6cddd370c865004fade217383fd86d","tid":531354,"uid":144323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"點解要住台北之後礁溪之後又台北？<br />\n<br />\n一開波落宜蘭玩完先上返台北<br />\n<br />\n幾米公園可以唔去，好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628d39f4bb9dcfaf24febfdb31791928a31efb61","tid":531354,"uid":1089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:21:08.000Z","msg":"Day4礁溪好難玩到一整天，主要係浸溫泉hea酒店多<br />\n原本都仲有個瀑布睇下但係頂層長期封住<br />\n<br />\n要係礁溪全日除非住老爺酒店啦，咁就可以三日唔出去都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外幾米公園半個鐘至一個鐘行晒，我果次睇左十分鐘唔夠就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a389ff06b7b16b4ddb59ebe5e0ecb95c273c1","tid":531354,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:26:18.000Z","msg":"台鐵如果要坐太魯閣或者普悠瑪既話你而家要開始BOOK定，全車對號同埋台北至花蓮好FULL<br />\n不過我更建議來回都坐客運，平過同埋舒服過台鐵"},{"pid":"b9821cdf2d981c20858b0d95316b27a8d801c83a","tid":531354,"uid":104360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a1024c6cd6cddd370c865004fade217383fd86d","tid":531354,"uid":144323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"點解要住台北之後礁溪之後又台北？<br />\n<br />\n一開波落宜蘭玩完先上返台北<br />\n<br />\n幾米公園可以唔去，好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"有諗過先去宜蘭再返台北<br />\n但星期六出發 好多酒店都千千聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且驚台鐵/客運好爆"},{"pid":"55168157ba6d79117c7c90b442a7c4ecc6d9e534","tid":531354,"uid":104360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff8a389ff06b7b16b4ddb59ebe5e0ecb95c273c1","tid":531354,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:26:18.000Z","msg":"台鐵如果要坐太魯閣或者普悠瑪既話你而家要開始BOOK定，全車對號同埋台北至花蓮好FULL<br />\n不過我更建議來回都坐客運，平過同埋舒服過台鐵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"因為同行友人唔太好客運 所以睇台鐵先<br />\n不過頭先諗住book去果程<br />\n發現想搭果班太魯閣已經full左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎真係要搭客運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbc37275cf41ad5c009eae1877ae88cfef0694c","tid":531354,"uid":104360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9849a307a33553bf4d2f7b68e8000d3270b960a","tid":531354,"uid":165801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"夜市去一個都夠啦 個個一樣"},{"pid":"b2762cc18b061907a340c079e4bd133e286797c1","tid":531354,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a1024c6cd6cddd370c865004fade217383fd86d","tid":531354,"uid":144323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"點解要住台北之後礁溪之後又台北？<br />\n<br />\n一開波落宜蘭玩完先上返台北<br />\n<br />\n幾米公園可以唔去，好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T22:26:20.000Z","msg":"但我都會揀中途去礁溪，因為可以放低大行李係台北，輕裝去礁溪、宜蘭比較方便"},{"pid":"b617574469e6eaec0e0696d798f8b0edd7a56715","tid":531354,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55168157ba6d79117c7c90b442a7c4ecc6d9e534","tid":531354,"uid":104360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff8a389ff06b7b16b4ddb59ebe5e0ecb95c273c1","tid":531354,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:26:18.000Z","msg":"台鐵如果要坐太魯閣或者普悠瑪既話你而家要開始BOOK定，全車對號同埋台北至花蓮好FULL<br />\n不過我更建議來回都坐客運，平過同埋舒服過台鐵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"因為同行友人唔太好客運 所以睇台鐵先<br />\n不過頭先諗住book去果程<br />\n發現想搭果班太魯閣已經full左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎真係要搭客運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T22:28:48.000Z","msg":"其實去礁溪搭客運好啲，時間快啲車又夠密，我上次去成車冇乜人差唔多包車咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2dcfb32a47c6f67b8937c43ffb0bb47f288370","tid":531354,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"有少少1999"},{"pid":"7e7d965181d782abbf3e5fe4c4327c0bfe959950","tid":531354,"uid":44550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"一去到台北就轉客運落礁溪會順d<br />\n宜蘭仲有whiskey廠, 同埋其他觀光工廠<br />\n頭城有得玩滑翔傘, 唔算貴.<br />\n落埋蘇澳仲有冷泉<br />\n<br />\n宜蘭, 礁溪, 蘇澳都airbnb 啦又平又抵住"},{"pid":"9e7011fca00b6a8ad7a7ca5a6c082810a216c33d","tid":531354,"uid":104360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"book哂酒店 改唔到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但黎緊成個台灣日日都落雨<br />\n邊到都唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d98963317ec62585f87c68c7bfe1a37db372e1","tid":531354,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"去咁多夜市...<br />\n<br />\n其實 d 夜市來來去去都係食果 d 野"},{"pid":"e1ea8a1650ac77f2cd9aaa8b138f90b1ece6c508","tid":531354,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d98963317ec62585f87c68c7bfe1a37db372e1","tid":531354,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"去咁多夜市...<br />\n<br />\n其實 d 夜市來來去去都係食果 d 野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T05:38:11.000Z","msg":"其實，隨心入一間餐廳食，可能仲有驚喜。<br />\n夜市當然無問題，不過可以唔一定局限只係幫襯夜市嘅。"}]}